      "date": "2018-03-01 14:28:42.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified+1\n\nTests uploaded by Onyx Autotest from onyx-30vm6 for review-dne-part-1 received by maloo, run on CentOS Linux 7/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/d47493d1-b8b4-4101-afbd-226a7194b6cc). Ran 6 tests. No failures.",
